<idea-plugin>
    <id>com.jack.plugin.autojson</id>
    <name>AutoJson</name>
    <version>1.1</version>
    <vendor email="luodijack@163.com" url="https://github.com/LuodiJackShen/AutoJson/tree/master">
        LuodiJackShen
    </vendor>

    <description><![CDATA[
      在flutter工程的bean类中自动生成json_serializable需要的序列化相关代码。<br>
      Generate the serialization-related code json_serializable needs automatically in the bean class of the flutter project.<br>
      <br><br>
      使用方式一(v1.1以上)：<br>
      1、打开.dart文件。<br>
      2、点击鼠标右键，选择 AutoJson，或者直接点击 Control+Enter (Windows:Alt+Insert)。<br>
      <br>
      使用方式二(v1.0以上)：<br>
      1、打开.dart文件，双击鼠标左键选择 .dart 文件的类名<b>（最新版本可不用双击选中类名）</b>。<br>
      2、点击鼠标右键，选择 AutoJson，或者直接点击 Control+Enter (Windows:Alt+Insert)。<br>
      <br><br>
      Final:<br>
      <a href="https://github.com/LuodiJackShen/AutoJson">GitHub repo</a>: https://github.com/LuodiJackShen/AutoJson <br>
      If you find a Bug or have some good ideas, please create a Issue in <a href="https://github.com/LuodiJackShen/AutoJson/issues/new">GitHub</a>
      <br><br>
      <a href="https://github.com/LuodiJackShen/AutoJson/blob/master/image/preview_high_quality.gif">操作演示：</a><br>
      <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuodiJackShen/AutoJson/master/image/v1.1_preview.gif">
      <br>
    ]]></description>

    <change-notes><![CDATA[
        - v1.1  ① 体验提升：不用选中类名即可生成需要的代码;② 功能限制：仅在 <b>xxx.dart</b> 文件中可用此插件。<br>
        - v1.0  实现基本功能:自动生成序列化需要的代码。<br>
    ]]>
    </change-notes>

    <!-- please see http://www.jetbrains.org/intellij/sdk/docs/basics/getting_started/build_number_ranges.html for description -->
    <idea-version since-build="173.0" />

    <!-- please see http://www.jetbrains.org/intellij/sdk/docs/basics/getting_started/plugin_compatibility.html
         on how to target different products -->
    <!-- uncomment to enable plugin in all products
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.lang</depends>
    -->

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <!-- Add your extensions here -->
    </extensions>

    <actions>
        <!-- Add your actions here -->
        <action id="AutoJson.GenerateAction" class="com.jack.Generate" text="AutoJson"
            description="com.jack.Generate code that json need automatically.">
            <add-to-group group-id="GenerateGroup" anchor="first" />
            <add-to-group group-id="EditMenu" anchor="first" />
            <add-to-group group-id="EditorPopupMenu" anchor="first" />
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="$default" first-keystroke="shift ctrl alt J" />
        </action>
    </actions>

</idea-plugin>
